"We have a spy working right now, on checking when the Autobots leave,
you will follow them. But first, we have some more troops to obtain."
One of the council Members says.

Slugslinger and Apeface move back from the angered Havotron, but
Spinister dosent seem disturbed. 

"Come now, there is no need for this Havotron" one of the Council
members adds.
::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
Motormaster turns and growls at Switchblade, cruel intentions flaring in
his eyes, "I'll feed you to the Terrorcons you little.." He is caught
off guard by a swing from Megatron, "You will do nothing to him."
Megatron turns his attention. "But I am sure he had a good reason
Switchblade. Motormaster is gruff, but not unstable like the other
Stunticons."
